name: Isis
description: This artwork is my tribute to the Egyptian goddess Isis. During a lucid dream I had once, Isis appeared to me. To talk of death and of living. Physical death is not the end of our journey. We need to try and live each lifetime with as much joy and resilience as we can, not holding on to the past or those we have lost. Artwork is an edited and animated image of handmade wool felt.
